Okay.

291
00:21:18,073 --> 00:21:20,446
Hozumi, you've really changed.

292
00:21:20,486 --> 00:21:21,447
Really?

293
00:21:21,460 --> 00:21:23,616
Yes, you look brighter.

294
00:21:24,685 --> 00:21:26,519
Someone has changed me.

295
00:21:27,271 --> 00:21:28,854
You mean, you're seeing someone?

296
00:21:29,756 --> 00:21:30,669
No.

297
00:21:32,290 --> 00:21:33,959
You're so easy to read.

298
00:21:35,928 --> 00:21:38,764
