Breaking up?

304
00:21:50,588 --> 00:21:52,278
I can accept that,

305
00:21:52,326 --> 00:21:54,180
but I can't go back to being friends.

306
00:21:55,293 --> 00:21:57,850
To be honest, I'm so lonely now.

307
00:21:58,458 --> 00:21:59,685
I see.

308
00:22:00,707 --> 00:22:02,822
If we break up...

309
00:22:05,053 --> 00:22:07,453
I'm so happy that I'm scared.

310
00:22:09,040 --> 00:22:10,830
If the time comes...

311
00:22:13,966 --> 00:22:16,135
Will I be able to bear it?

