This happiness

314
00:23:12,354 --> 00:23:15,007
(disappeared...)
could just disappear one day.

315
00:23:16,040 --> 00:23:17,763
Loving someone,

316
00:23:17,763 --> 00:23:19,199
(The future we choose...)
in my opinion, means accepting.

317
00:23:19,199 --> 00:23:21,292
